{"tid":1020680,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[Google Map支援]日本 新宿橫濱鐮倉江之島8日7夜hea游計劃","createTime":"2019-02-13T18:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T17:57:41.000Z","uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7407b6b1b014b1a1c0052d94382ff217e081be6a","tid":1020680,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:32:26.000Z","msg":"本人鐘意行下睇下 所以編排多愛行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新宿篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 1</span><br />\n3點鐘到著日本成田機場<br />\n6點左右到酒店 搞呢搞路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8XBb6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8XBb6v.png&h=d630ea5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍點為酒店位置 都幾近JR大久保站<br />\n打算用Suica 搭JR山手線算算<br />\n8點左右落原宿 去食飯同行竹下通嗰邊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 2</span><br />\n11點左右岀發落渋谷睇下忠犬像 再落行下附近主要係行金王八幡宮<br />\n午飯前後應該就走得 落原宿/新宿行埋Day1行唔切嘅地方<br />\n夜晚翻新宿 晚飯及行附近。<br />\n註 有冇咩景點大家推介下？各駅以東區域為主<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 3</span><br />\n12點前Check out 搭湘南新宿線落橫濱<br />\n3點左右到 Check In<br />\n4,5點酒店近日之岀町站，要搭京急本線去新高島行橫濱Landmark <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vpK73iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpK73iS.png&h=68778f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢日應該冇乜野做 可能會行翻去日之岀町嗰邊附近睇一日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 4</span><br />\n朝早可能行過去關內<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESMVsNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESMVsNN.png&h=5087e94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話13分鐘 都唔知信唔信佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway去到橫濱公園休息下<br />\n3點左右之後落元町<br />\n期望入夜7，8點可以去到山下公園<br />\n回程都係行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhUjUtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhUjUtQ.png&h=39d61306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鎌倉篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 5</span><br />\n11點左右Check out 搭橫須賀線去鎌倉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSN9xhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSN9xhG.png&h=09cc9fac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmejUv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmejUv2.png&h=23709e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到達可能2，3點 買兩張江之電pass後行去酒店<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fbm7Sd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fbm7Sd.png&h=7a947f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又話八分鐘 信唔信得過架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3，4點到就食野，再上鶴岡八幡宮<br />\n6，7點落小町行<br />\n之後翻酒店。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">江之島篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 6</span><br />\n早上Checkout 用第一張江之電pass去江之島駅<br />\n到達大概1，2點 Check in後<br />\n我就可以決定沿江之電上去(湘南海岸公園駅)<br />\n還是行過去片瀨江之島(圖)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yh6m7UM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYh6m7UM.png&h=95a883b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求意見<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 7</span><br />\n全日登江之島<br />\n會hea足全日 反正佢就係我再飛嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 8</span><br />\n早上Checkout <br />\n希望極樂寺同御靈神社有地方放行李<br />\n3點左右乘江電到鐮倉<br />\n再搭橫須賀線到千葉轉乘成田線去機場<br />\n到著大概6點 8點機<br />\n就完了<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得需要一d pass尤其係翻成田嗰度 250蚊hkd<br />\n同埋行程都可以再執 我編得比較鬆<br />\n求意見 狠評<br />\n第一次自己一個人去，乜都自己plan 好驚<br />\n各位巴絲有冇想知 我一定會儘量講 Thank you!"},{"pid":"74a876d0db562c728ff7366b6e3972fce2f984d2","tid":1020680,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af13c78295cadb3e2ab941e5475bd84bee52a9ac","tid":1020680,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"希望沖完個涼有人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好需要建議。。"},{"pid":"f8a80f6fad4dc6d34b0285d78bf8dfe2653b159a","tid":1020680,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"行下睇下就咪鬼去東京啦"},{"pid":"a456823ce25c4991cb2c69d2343b55087071f46a","tid":1020680,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a80f6fad4dc6d34b0285d78bf8dfe2653b159a","tid":1020680,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"行下睇下就咪鬼去東京啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"所以咪去埋橫濱鐮倉江之島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4a85e78a5b06f3817d757b0c92d214ef7f5bdb","tid":1020680,"uid":223866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7407b6b1b014b1a1c0052d94382ff217e081be6a","tid":1020680,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:32:26.000Z","msg":"本人鐘意行下睇下 所以編排多愛行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新宿篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 1</span><br />\n3點鐘到著日本成田機場<br />\n6點左右到酒店 搞呢搞路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8XBb6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8XBb6v.png&h=d630ea5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍點為酒店位置 都幾近JR大久保站<br />\n打算用Suica 搭JR山手線算算<br />\n8點左右落原宿 去食飯同行竹下通嗰邊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 2</span><br />\n11點左右岀發落渋谷睇下忠犬像 再落行下附近主要係行金王八幡宮<br />\n午飯前後應該就走得 落原宿/新宿行埋Day1行唔切嘅地方<br />\n夜晚翻新宿 晚飯及行附近。<br />\n註 有冇咩景點大家推介下？各駅以東區域為主<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 3</span><br />\n12點前Check out 搭湘南新宿線落橫濱<br />\n3點左右到 Check In<br />\n4,5點酒店近日之岀町站，要搭京急本線去新高島行橫濱Landmark <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vpK73iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpK73iS.png&h=68778f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢日應該冇乜野做 可能會行翻去日之岀町嗰邊附近睇一日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 4</span><br />\n朝早可能行過去關內<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESMVsNN.png\" data-thumbna